{"id":"sonic-mega-workflow-001","meta":{"instanceId":"captchasonic-mega-workflow"},"name":"Solve any image CAPTCHA with CaptchaSonic","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"fb326115-1f23-46ed-86dd-96a3a9790d2a","name":"Sticky Note","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-1104,-944],"parameters":{"width":480,"height":896,"content":"## Solve any image CAPTCHA with CaptchaSonic\n\n### How it works\n\nThis workflow exposes a webhook that accepts CAPTCHA-solving requests, validates the incoming payload, and routes it to the appropriate CaptchaSonic solver based on the CAPTCHA type. Each solver branch handles a different image or classification challenge, then successful results are normalized and returned to the caller. Unsupported or invalid routes are returned through a separate error response path.\n\n### Setup steps\n\n- Configure the Webhook CAPTCHA Trigger with the desired HTTP method, path, and response mode for your n8n instance.\n- Add CaptchaSonic credentials/API key to each CaptchaSonic solver node and verify the selected operation matches the expected CAPTCHA type.\n- Ensure incoming webhook requests include the fields expected by Validate Request and Route to Solver, such as CAPTCHA type plus image data, site key, or challenge metadata as needed.\n- Test both a supported CAPTCHA request and an unsupported/invalid request to confirm the success and error webhook responses are formatted correctly.\n\n### Customization\n\nAdjust the validation code, switch routing rules, and Format Solution output schema to match your client application. Additional CaptchaSonic branches can be added to the solver column for new CAPTCHA types."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"e1dd07ed-8bf0-4da4-9d14-201e37881d5c","name":"Sticky Note1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-544,-128],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":848,"height":560,"content":"## Receive and route request\n\nEntry cluster that accepts the webhook call, validates the payload, and chooses which solver branch should handle the CAPTCHA request."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"c5686aa9-2189-4919-8be6-2a3cdafd4c58","name":"Sticky Note2","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[480,-944],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":240,"height":784,"content":"## Upper solver branches\n\nTop portion of the CaptchaSonic solver column for image-to-text, reCAPTCHA v2 classification, and PopularCaptcha classification requests."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"d1761767-a8da-4620-9ff4-3b83072f2ac4","name":"Sticky Note3","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[480,-128],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":240,"height":736,"content":"## Middle solver branches\n\nCentral CaptchaSonic solver cluster for AWS WAF, BLS/OCR, and TikTok CAPTCHA challenges."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"af541e1b-c0a5-4a83-8a55-30239c7c606d","name":"Sticky Note4","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[752,304],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":240,"height":544,"content":"## Lower solver branches\n\nLower CaptchaSonic solver cluster for Binance CAPTCHA and general vision-engine based challenges."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"782b004d-064b-471c-a580-0f7c4030422e","name":"Sticky Note5","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[880,-240],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":448,"height":496,"content":"## Format and respond\n\nOutput cluster that normalizes successful solver results and sends either the final solution or an error response back to the webhook caller."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"cb168a5d-4b3f-4d07-b202-54d675b12d01","name":"When CAPTCHA Submitted","type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[-496,0],"webhookId":"8375adf5-b652-4d1d-8dac-b7e057d6ee63","parameters":{"path":"captchasonic-solve","options":{},"httpMethod":"POST","responseMode":"responseNode"},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"508d0026-d58c-4836-b19f-b480a5d4e09e","name":"Validate CAPTCHA Request","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-208,0],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const input = $input.first().json;\nconst body = input.body;\n\nif (!body || typeof body !== 'object') {\n  return [{ json: { _outputIndex: 9, _error: 'Request body must be a JSON object' } }];\n}\nif (!body.type || typeof body.type !== 'string' || !body.type.trim()) {\n  return [{ json: { _outputIndex: 9, _error: 'Missing required field: type. Supported: imagetotext, recaptchav2, popularcaptcha, awswaf, blsocr, tiktok, binance, visionengine' } }];\n}\n\nconst type = body.type.trim().toLowerCase();\n\nconst types = {\n  imagetotext: { idx: 0, required: [\"image\"], optional: [\"module\", \"websiteURL\", \"question\"] },\n  recaptchav2: { idx: 1, required: [\"image\", \"question\"], optional: [\"websiteURL\", \"imageBackground\"] },\n  popularcaptcha: { idx: 2, required: [\"image\", \"question\"], optional: [\"websiteURL\", \"websiteKey\", \"imageBackground\", \"body\"] },\n  awswaf: { idx: 3, required: [\"image\", \"question\"], optional: [\"websiteURL\", \"imageBackground\"] },\n  blsocr: { idx: 4, required: [\"image\"], optional: [\"module\", \"websiteURL\", \"question\"] },\n  tiktok: { idx: 5, required: [\"image\"], optional: [\"websiteURL\", \"question\", \"imageBackground\"] },\n  binance: { idx: 6, required: [\"image\"], optional: [\"websiteURL\", \"question\", \"imageBackground\"] },\n  visionengine: { idx: 7, required: [\"image\"], optional: [\"websiteURL\", \"question\", \"imageBackground\"] },\n};\n\nconst config = types[type];\nif (!config) {\n  return [{ json: { _outputIndex: 9, _error: 'Unsupported type: ' + body.type + '. Supported: ' + Object.keys(types).join(', ') } }];\n}\n\nconst missing = config.required.filter(f => !body[f] && body[f] !== false && body[f] !== 0);\nif (missing.length > 0) {\n  return [{ json: { _outputIndex: 9, _error: 'Type \"' + type + '\" requires: ' + missing.join(', ') + '. Optional: ' + (config.optional.join(', ') || 'none') } }];\n}\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...input, body: { ...body, type }, _outputIndex: config.idx } }];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"bf380ffc-ec7d-4a86-8da7-7c184fcfb51e","name":"Route by CAPTCHA Type","type":"n8n-nodes-base.switch","position":[160,0],"parameters":{"mode":"expression","output":"={{ $json._outputIndex }}","numberOutputs":10},"typeVersion":3.4},{"id":"da5250c9-3b41-42f2-8bec-3481220aa2fb","name":"Solve Image Text CAPTCHA","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[528,-720],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"ImageToTextTask","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"Image To Text","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"ea31b6dc-6e50-402e-9dbf-4a91ab572e61","name":"Solve reCAPTCHA v2","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[528,-520],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"ReCaptchaV2Image","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"reCAPTCHA v2 Classification","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"e2147342-8941-4b58-a590-42518afcd45d","name":"Solve PopularCaptcha Type","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[528,-320],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"PopularCaptchaImage","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"PopularCaptcha Classification","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"aa15880d-7953-4063-81a8-80d80aa9b036","name":"Solve AWS WAF CAPTCHA","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[528,64],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"AwsWafClassification","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"AWS WAF Classification","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"06a2e2e1-75df-455d-ad4a-d01f5baaf910","name":"Solve BLS OCR CAPTCHA","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[528,256],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"OcrImage","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"BLS / OCR","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"88286bee-1731-41dd-94af-222809dabb83","name":"Solve TikTok CAPTCHA","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[528,464],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"tiktokClassification","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"TikTok CAPTCHA","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"c9b62707-6528-4b03-82ad-c1412436cc50","name":"Solve Binance CAPTCHA","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[800,480],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"BinanceTask","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"Binance CAPTCHA","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"9d5f48a4-73b7-4f22-84c1-5013ec2bb75e","name":"Solve Vision Engine CAPTCHA","type":"n8n-nodes-captchasonic.captchaSonic","onError":"continueRegularOutput","position":[800,688],"parameters":{"body":"={{ $json.body.extraFields ? JSON.stringify($json.body.extraFields) : '{}' }}","type":"VisionEngine","image":"={{ $json.body.image || '' }}","question":"={{ $json.body.question || '' }}","resource":"Recognition","operation":"Vision Engine","websiteURL":"={{ $json.body.websiteURL || '' }}"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"5697974b-8493-458d-834f-13ce1a76359a","name":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[928,-16],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const input = $input.first().json;\nif (input.error || !input.data) {\n  const errorMsg = input.error\n    ? (typeof input.error === 'string' ? input.error : (input.error.message || JSON.stringify(input.error)))\n    : 'No solution returned';\n  return [{ json: { success: false, error: errorMsg } }];\n}\nreturn [{ json: {\n  success: true,\n  type: $('When CAPTCHA Submitted').item.json.body.type,\n  solution: input.data.solution || input.data,\n  solvedAt: new Date().toISOString()\n}}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"0a85a0ce-aa59-4d55-b522-2f5bfd49b902","name":"Send CAPTCHA Solution","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","position":[1184,-80],"parameters":{"options":{},"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ JSON.stringify($json) }}"},"typeVersion":1.5},{"id":"1652aece-1483-41f8-9300-a180af0862da","name":"Send Error Response","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","position":[1184,96],"parameters":{"options":{"responseCode":400},"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ JSON.stringify({ error: $json._error || 'Unknown error', supportedTypes: ['imagetotext','recaptchav2','popularcaptcha','awswaf','blsocr','tiktok','binance','visionengine'] }) }}"},"typeVersion":1.5}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"connections":{"Solve reCAPTCHA v2":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Solve TikTok CAPTCHA":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by CAPTCHA Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Solve Image Text CAPTCHA","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Solve reCAPTCHA v2","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Solve PopularCaptcha Type","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Solve AWS WAF CAPTCHA","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Solve BLS OCR CAPTCHA","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Solve TikTok CAPTCHA","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Solve Binance CAPTCHA","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Solve Vision Engine CAPTCHA","type":"main","index":0}],[],[{"node":"Send Error Response","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Solve AWS WAF CAPTCHA":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Solve BLS OCR CAPTCHA":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Solve Binance CAPTCHA":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"When CAPTCHA Submitted":{"main":[[{"node":"Validate CAPTCHA Request","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Format CAPTCHA Solution":{"main":[[{"node":"Send CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Solve Image Text CAPTCHA":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Validate CAPTCHA Request":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by CAPTCHA Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Solve PopularCaptcha Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Solve Vision Engine CAPTCHA":{"main":[[{"node":"Format CAPTCHA Solution","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}